comment: Builder class for custom chat or chat intent.

withAudioCallCapability.comment: Audio call capability means that you can initialize an audio call from chat activity.

parameters.callOptions: call options for the call from the chat UI such as recording,...
parameters.callCapabilities: call capabilities such as whiteboard,file sharing, ...     * @return ChatIntentOptions

tags.parameters: call capabilities such as whiteboard,file sharing, ...     * @return ChatIntentOptions

withAudioUpgradableCallCapability.comment:
Audio call capability means that you can initialize an audio/video call from chat activity.
Upgradable means that the call will be initialized as audio call but can be
upgraded to video if selected camera button from call action items.

parameters.callOptions: call options for the call from the chat UI such as recording,...
parameters.callCapabilities: call capabilities such as whiteboard,file sharing, ...

tags.parameters: call capabilities such as whiteboard,file sharing, ...

withAudioVideoCallCapability.comment: Audio video call capability means that you can initialize a video call from chat activity.
